[div class=p 
	[em 
		"Tom and Jerry: The Movie
	]em
	" is a video game for the Sega Master System and the Game Gear that has the same name as the 1992 animated movie. While it may have share the name and stars classic cartoon stars Tom and Jerry, the game has nothing to do with the movie. You play as Tom as he chases Jerry across various settings, with various obstacles and puzzles impeding Tom. Eventually, Tom will corner Jerry and catch him, but he can catch him much sooner than that.
